name: priceviewer.com, WalMart Store Locations, USA, 2007
description: This is a map of the locations of all of the WalMart stores throughout the United States. This dataset geocodes the street address of the Walmarts and shows their locations on the map along with their phone numbers for more information. This data was found at a Walmart Locations website which aggregated the locations by state. here is our Source for the information: http://www.priceviewer.com/walmart_locations/
